cienaCesIclMIB.name: cienaCesIclMIB
cienaCesIclMIB.contactinfo: Mib Meister 115 North Sullivan Road Spokane Valley, WA 99037 USA Phone: +1 509 242 9000 Email: support@ciena.com
cienaCesIclMIB.description: This MIB defines the managed objects for Inter-chassis Links

cienaCesIclTable.name: cienaCesIclTable
cienaCesIclTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing all the Inter-chassis Links (ICLs).

cienaCesIclEntry.name: cienaCesIclEntry
cienaCesIclEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the cienaCesIclTable.

cienaCesIclName.name: cienaCesIclName
cienaCesIclName.description: This object specifies the name of the Inter-chassis link (ICL).

cienaCesIclRemoteMacAddress.name: cienaCesIclRemoteMacAddress
cienaCesIclRemoteMacAddress.description: This object specifies the Inter-chassis link remote MAC address.

cienaCesIclType.name: cienaCesIclType
cienaCesIclType.description: This object specifies the Inter-chassis link type.

cienaCesIclVlan.name: cienaCesIclVlan
cienaCesIclVlan.description: This object specifies the ICL VLAN. This is valid only if cienaCesIclType is vlan(1).

cienaCesIclVsName.name: cienaCesIclVsName
cienaCesIclVsName.description: This object specifies the ICL VS. This is valid only if cienaCesIclType is vs(2).

cienaCesIclCfmServicePrimary.name: cienaCesIclCfmServicePrimary
cienaCesIclCfmServicePrimary.description: This object specifies primary CFM service on the ICL.

cienaCesIclCfmServiceSecondary.name: cienaCesIclCfmServiceSecondary
cienaCesIclCfmServiceSecondary.description: This object specifies the name of the Inter-chassis link (ICL).

cienaCesIclOperState.name: cienaCesIclOperState
cienaCesIclOperState.description: This object specifies the ICL operational state.

cienaCesIclStatus.name: cienaCesIclStatus
cienaCesIclStatus.description: This object specifies the status of the ICL.

cienaCesIclAdminState.name: cienaCesIclAdminState
cienaCesIclAdminState.description: This object specifies the admin state of the ICL.

cienaCesIclCfmFault.name: cienaCesIclCfmFault
cienaCesIclCfmFault.description: This object specifies if CFM fault is set on the ICL.

cienaCesIclVplsFault.name: cienaCesIclVplsFault
cienaCesIclVplsFault.description: This object specifies if VPLS fault is set on the ICL.

cienaCesIclRxTimeout.name: cienaCesIclRxTimeout
cienaCesIclRxTimeout.description: This object specifies if Rx timeout fault is set on the ICL

cienaCesIclIntervalMismatch.name: cienaCesIclIntervalMismatch
cienaCesIclIntervalMismatch.description: This object specifies if interval mismatch fault is set on the ICL

cienaCesIclHeartbeatInterval.name: cienaCesIclHeartbeatInterval
cienaCesIclHeartbeatInterval.description: This object specifies the ICL heartbeat interval. The range is 1 to 30s and the default is 1s.

cienaCesIclUpTime.name: cienaCesIclUpTime
cienaCesIclUpTime.description: This object specifies total time for which the ICL has been operationally down.

cienaCesIclTotalDownTime.name: cienaCesIclTotalDownTime
cienaCesIclTotalDownTime.description: This object specifies total time for which the ICL has been operationally down.

cienaCesIclRxFrames.name: cienaCesIclRxFrames
cienaCesIclRxFrames.description: This object specifies the number of CICP frames received by the ICL.

cienaCesIclTxFrames.name: cienaCesIclTxFrames
cienaCesIclTxFrames.description: This object specifies the number of CICP frames transmitted by the ICL.

cienaCesIclRxUnknownFrames.name: cienaCesIclRxUnknownFrames
cienaCesIclRxUnknownFrames.description: This object specifies the number of unknown frames received by the ICL.

cienaCesIclRxHtbtFrames.name: cienaCesIclRxHtbtFrames
cienaCesIclRxHtbtFrames.description: This object specifies the number of Hearbeat frames received by the ICL.

cienaCesIclTxHtbtFrames.name: cienaCesIclTxHtbtFrames
cienaCesIclTxHtbtFrames.description: This object specifies the number of Hearbeat frames transmitted by the ICL.

cienaCesIclTxFailedFrames.name: cienaCesIclTxFailedFrames
cienaCesIclTxFailedFrames.description: This object specifies the number of failed to transmit frames.

cienaCesIclNumberFailures.name: cienaCesIclNumberFailures
cienaCesIclNumberFailures.description: This object specifies the number of ICL failures.

cienaCesIclRxConfigMismatch.name: cienaCesIclRxConfigMismatch
cienaCesIclRxConfigMismatch.description: This object specifies the number of ICL config mismatch frames received.

cienaCesIclStateChange.name: cienaCesIclStateChange
cienaCesIclStateChange.description: This notification is sent when ICL oper state changes. Var binding cienaCesIclIndex represents the ICL index.
